"C:\Dev\matlab-functions\tables\phi1_map_observable_candidates.csv","3","shoulder_compensation,""deltaS(x,T)=S(x,T)-S_peak(T)*CDF(P_T)(x); x as above. Use same x_ridge. Observable: O2(T)=∫_{x_min..x_max, |x|>x_ridge} deltaS(x,T) dx (i.e., total integral minus ridge integral on the canonical x-grid)."",kappa1(T),-1,-1,3.38159859309e-17,""x_ridge scaled by 0.8..1.2 => Pearson=[-1,-1], Spearman=[-1,-1], LOOCV_RMSE=[2.46957e-17,3.86860e-17] (idealized Phi1-rank1 residual evaluation)"",PARTIAL but useful signature"
"C:\Dev\matlab-functions\tables\phi1_map_observable_candidates.csv","4","ridge_centered_second_moment,""Use same deltaS and x_ridge. Observable: O3(T)=∫_{-x_ridge}^{x_ridge} x^2 * deltaS(x,T) dx."",kappa1(T),1,1,2.16666892705e-17,""x_ridge scaled by 0.8..1.2 => Pearson=[1,1], Spearman=[1,1], LOOCV_RMSE=[2.15739e-17,3.35180e-17] (idealized Phi1-rank1 residual evaluation)"",PARTIAL but useful signature"
"C:\Dev\matlab-functions\tables\phi1_map_observable_candidates.csv","5","lobe_balance_center_minus_shoulders,""Use same deltaS and x_ridge; let x_min=-x_max from the canonical x-grid. Define ridge mean m_r(T)=O1(T)/(2*x_ridge) and shoulder mean m_s(T)=O2(T)/( (x_max-x_min) - 2*x_ridge ). Observable: O4(T)=m_r(T)-m_s(T)."",kappa1(T),1,1,3.39934988878e-17,""x_ridge scaled by 0.8..1.2 => Pearson=[1,1], Spearman=[1,1], LOOCV_RMSE=[1.88971e-17,3.39935e-17] (idealized Phi1-rank1 residual evaluation)"",PARTIAL but useful signature"
"C:\Dev\matlab-functions\tables\phi1_map_observable_candidates.csv","6","matched_symmetric_gaussian_kernel,""Use deltaS(x,T) and x from the canonical grid. Choose sigma from ridge width: sigma = x_ridge/2 with the same x_ridge above. Observable: O5(T)=∫_{x_min..x_max} deltaS(x,T)*exp(-x^2/(2*sigma^2)) dx."",kappa1(T),1,1,3.64979663114e-17,""x_ridge scaled by 0.8..1.2 => Pearson=[1,1], Spearman=[1,1], LOOCV_RMSE=[3.00463e-17,4.92287e-17] (idealized Phi1-rank1 residual evaluation)"",PARTIAL but useful signature"
